        <updateDate>2018-06-29T19:16:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Cooperate with Law Enforcement Agencies and Watch Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill limits a financial institution's liability for maintaining a customer account in compliance with a written request by a federal, state, tribal, or local law enforcement agency. A federal or state agency may not take an adverse supervisory action against a financial institution with respect to maintaining an account consistent with such a request. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
